description:
English translation of the Japanese manga Galaxy Angel II (ギャラクシーエンジェルII 天使の羽根休め).

Several years after Milfeulle and the Angel Troupe led by Takuto Meyers defeated Eonia's forces in EDEN...

A new galaxy called NEUE is found, and Milfeulle is now the gatekeeper of the "gate" that connects EDEN and NEUE. The Moon Angel Troupe has disbanded, and each of the former Moon Angel Troupe members work for the expansion into NEUE.

Apricot Sakuraba is a member of the Lune Angel Troupe, and Kazuya Shiranami from NEUE was selected to join the new Angel Troupe. Their mission is to find other "gates" and "gatekeepers."
name: Galaxy Angel II

description:
English translation of the Japanese manga Galaxy Angel (ギャラクシーエンジェル).

The Angel Troupe is composed of five beautiful and talented female pilots.

When a coup d’état threatens the life of Prince Shiva, they are called to action. Takuto Meyers is put in charge of the Angels and is ordered to escort Prince Shiva to safety.

With their enemy right behind them, Takuto and the Angels have enough to worry about—but multiple love triangles don’t seem to be helping!
name: Galaxy Angel

description:
English translation of the Japanese manga Galaxy Angel 2nd (ギャラクシーエンジェル2nd).

Now that Chitose is on the team, the Angel Troupe needs her to join them for a very special mission: a Galaxy Angel vacation!

As Milfeulle and the gang get acquainted with their new teammate, the Elle Ciel is fitted with a new weapon from the White Moon.

What is this strange piece of Lost Technology? Can Takuto figure out how to use it? With Milfie's luck, they'd better figure it out soon!
name: Galaxy Angel Beta

description:
English translation of the Japanese manga Galaxy Angel - Parody Daibakuhatsu!! (ギャラクシーエンジェル パロディ).

The Angel Troupe is just about done with their current mission to deliver over a million dollars to the Bank of Transbaal, when Milfeulle accidentally opens the hatch and loses it in space. In order to keep their jobs, the Angel Troupe needs to raise money, and fast!

Read this and other exciting adventures by some of Japan’s most talented artists!
name: Galaxy Angel Party
